OL,3,C'I've let him down': Mum's two-year
OL,4,Cwait for justice over son's killing
OL,6,FNo-one has ever been charged.
OL,8,FHis mother Delia Prudence said: "We
OL,9,Fgot told the worst news that he was
OL,10,Factually brain dead and there was
OL,11,Fnothing they could do so they just
OL,12,Fswitched the machine off and that was
OL,13,Fit, he was gone.
OL,15,F"I just feel that I've let John down
OL,16,Fbecause I can't get any answers.
OL,18,F"It's like part of me has died. I'm
OL,19,Fjust frustrated and heartbroken
OL,20,Fbecause there was no need for him to
OL,21,Fdie.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
