OL,3,C'I've let him down': Mum's two-year
OL,4,Cwait for justice over son's killing
OL,6,FHowever, he was found unresponsive a
OL,7,Fmonth later and was declared brain
OL,8,Fdead on 11 December 2023. He left
OL,9,Fbehind daughter Robyn, who was eight
OL,10,Fat the time.
OL,12,FMrs Prudence said: "Me and the family
OL,13,Fand his daughter especially, she's
OL,14,Fgoing to be asking questions when she
OL,15,Fgets older. She understands what's
OL,16,Fhappened to a degree but she's only a
OL,17,Fchild still and she's got to grow up
OL,18,Fwithout a real dad."
