OL,3,C'I've let him down': Mum's two-year
OL,4,Cwait for justice over son's killing
OL,6,FJohn's step-father Phillip Prudence
OL,7,Fsaid: "Every day you are just hoping
OL,8,Fhe is going to walk through the door.
OL,9,FHe should be here now. But I don't
OL,10,Fknow what ran through their minds when
OL,11,Fthey did it.
OL,13,F"He was good as gold, he had a heart
OL,14,Fof gold."
OL,16,FA 26-year-old man was initially
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,18,Fmurder in connection with the assault
OL,19,Fin Silver Street. He was later
OL,20,Freleased on police bail pending
OL,21,Ffurther enquiries.
